Class LevelParent

java.lang.Object
com.example.demo.levels.LevelParent
All Implemented Interfaces:
InputManager.ProjectileFiredListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
LevelBoss, LevelOne, LevelTwo
public abstract class LevelParent extends Object implements InputManager.ProjectileFiredListener
The Level Parent is an abstract class that represent a level in the game. Manages the game state, actors, and interactions within a level.
